### Textualize.io Position Example (CSS)

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/styles/position

Provides the CSS to style widgets for positioning in Textualize.io. This example defines styles for a screen and two labels, one with absolute positioning and another with relative positioning.

```css
Screen {
    align: center middle;
}

Label {
    padding: 1;
    background: $panel;
    border: thick $border;
}

Label#label1 {
    position: absolute;
    offset: 2 1;
}

Label#label2 {
    position: relative;
    offset: 2 1;
}


```

