### Mount Welcome Widget on Key Press in Textual

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/guide/app

Illustrates mounting a `Welcome` widget in response to any key press. Multiple key presses can mount multiple instances of the widget. The `on_button_pressed` method is included to allow exiting the application.

```python
from textual.app import App
from textual.widgets import Welcome


class WelcomeApp(App):
    def on_key(self) -> None:
        self.mount(Welcome())

    def on_button_pressed(self) -> None:
        self.exit()


if __name__ == "__main__":
    app = WelcomeApp()
    app.run()

```

