### Textual - CSS Example for Text Wrapping

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/styles/text_wrap

Provides CSS examples for the text-wrap style in Textual. It illustrates how to set text-wrap to 'wrap' (default behavior) and 'nowrap' (disabling wrapping) for different elements.

```css
Static {
    height: 1fr;
}

#static1 {
    text-wrap: wrap; /* this is the default */
    background: blue 20%;
}
#static2 {
    text-wrap: nowrap; /* disable wrapping */
    background: green 20%;
}


```

```css
text-wrap: wrap;
text-wrap: nowrap;


```

