### Delete Text API

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/widgets/text_area

Deletes text within a specified range (start and end locations) in the document.

```APIDOC
## POST /websites/textual_textualize_io/delete

### Description
Deletes the text between two locations in the document.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/websites/textual_textualize_io/delete

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **start** (Location) - Required - The starting location of the text to delete.
- **end** (Location) - Required - The ending location of the text to delete.
- **maintain_selection_offset** (bool) - Optional - If True, the selection offset is maintained. Defaults to True.

### Request Example
{
  "start": {
    "row": 5,
    "column": 0
  },
  "end": {
    "row": 5,
    "column": 10
  },
  "maintain_selection_offset": true
}

### Response
#### Success Response (200)
- **edit_result** (EditResult) - An EditResult containing information about the edit.

#### Response Example
{
  "edit_result": {
    "cursor_updated": true,
    "selection_updated": false
  }
}
```

