### Benchmarking Tuple Creation Speed (pyinstrument)

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/blog/2023/09/18/things-i-learned-while-building-textuals-textarea

A command-line benchmark using hyperfine to measure the time taken to create 10,000 standard tuple objects in Python. This serves as a performance comparison against NamedTuples.

```bash
โฏ hyperfine -w 2 'python sandbox/darren/make_tuples.py'
Benchmark 1: python sandbox/darren/make_tuples.py
