### Styling Labels in Textual (Pre-0.38.0 vs 0.38.0)

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/blog/2023/09/21/textual-0380-adds-a-syntax-aware-textarea

Demonstrates the difference in CSS specificity for styling nested elements in Textual. The first example shows the verbose method used before version 0.38.0 to target labels within a dark mode widget. The second example shows the more concise and readable syntax introduced in 0.38.0 using the :dark pseudo-selector.

```css
/* Pre-0.38.0 */
App.-dark-mode MyWidget Label {
    ...
}

```

```css
/* 0.38.0 and later */
MyWidget:dark Label {
    ...
}

```

