### Initialize and Use ProgressBar Widget

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/widgets/progress_bar

This snippet demonstrates how to create a ProgressBar widget, set its total, and advance its progress in a Textual application. It requires the 'ProgressBar' class and 'App' base class.

```python
class MyApp(App):
    def compose(self):
        yield ProgressBar(total=100)

    def key_space(self):
        self.query_one(ProgressBar).advance(5)
```

