### CSS: Setting Maximum Widget Width

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/styles/max_width

Provides CSS examples for setting the `max-width` property. It demonstrates setting a maximum width in terms of rows (height units) and as a percentage of the viewport width.

```css
/* Set the maximum width to 10 rows */
max-width: 10;

/* Set the maximum width to 25% of the viewport width */
max-width: 25vw;


```

