### Get Shown Keys Property

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/api/binding

The `shown_keys` property of `BindingsMap` returns a list of all `Binding` objects that are configured to be visible (i.e., their `show` attribute is `True`). This is useful for rendering UI elements like footers.

```python
shown_keys
```

