### Get a Built-in Textual TextArea Theme

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/widgets/text_area

This code shows how to retrieve a reference to one of Textual's pre-defined themes using the `get_builtin_theme` classmethod. This is useful for extending or inspecting existing themes.

```python
from textual.widgets.text_area import TextAreaTheme

monokai = TextAreaTheme.get_builtin_theme("monokai")
```

