### Get Pane Method in Textualize IO

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/widgets/tabbed_content

Retrieves the 'TabPane' widget associated with a given ID or 'ContentTab'. Raises 'ValueError' if no ID is available.

```python
get_pane(pane_id)
```

