### Action Switch Mode

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/api/app

Switches the application to a specified mode.

```APIDOC
## action_switch_mode

### Description
An action that switches to the given mode.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/websites/textual_textualize_io/action_switch_mode

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **mode** (str) - Required - The mode to switch to.

### Request Example
{
  "action": "action_switch_mode",
  "mode": "my_mode"
}

### Response
#### Success Response (200)
- **status** (str) - Indicates success or failure of the action.

#### Response Example
{
  "status": "success"
}
```

