An action to simulate a key press. This will invoke the same actions as if the user had pressed the key.

### Method
POST

### Endpoint
/websites/textual_textualize_io/action_simulate_key

### Parameters
#### Request Body
- **key** (str) - Required - The key to process.

### Request Example
{
  "action": "action_simulate_key",
  "key": "enter"
}

### Response
#### Success Response (200)
- **status** (str) - Indicates success or failure of the action.

#### Response Example
{
  "status": "success"
}
```

