### Stylize Content with Bold Text

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/guide/content

Shows how to apply styling to a portion of Content using the stylize method. It creates content with 'Hello, World!' and then bolds the word 'World'.

```python
content = Content("Hello, World!")
content = content.stylize(7, 12, "bold")

```

