### Temporarily Prevent Message Types (Python)

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/api/message_pump

A context manager that temporarily prevents specified message types from being posted. This is useful for ensuring atomic operations where certain updates should not trigger intermediate events. Example shows preventing 'Input.Changed' events.

```python
with self.prevent(Input.Changed):
    input.value = "foo"
```

