### Get App Return Code (Python)

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/api/app

Retrieves the exit return code of the Textual application. A non-zero value indicates an error, with 1 signifying a fatal error. The value is None if the app has not yet exited. This property can be used with `sys.exit`.

```python
import sys
my_app.run()
sys.exit(my_app.return_code)
```

