### Generate System Commands for Command Palette

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/api/app

Provides a generator yielding `SystemCommand` instances for use in the command palette. This method can be implemented in app subclasses to add custom commands, and requires `SystemCommandsProvider` to be in `App.COMMANDS`.

```python
get_system_commands(screen)
```

```python
def get_system_commands(self, screen: Screen) -> Iterable[SystemCommand]:
    yield from super().get_system_commands(screen)
    yield SystemCommand("Bell", "Ring the bell", self.bell)
```

