### Toggle Line Numbers in Textual TextArea Gutter

Source: https://textual.textualize.io/widgets/text_area

This code shows how to control the visibility of line numbers in the gutter of a Textual TextArea. Setting `show_line_numbers` to `True` or `False` will immediately update the widget's appearance. The starting line number can also be adjusted with `line_number_start`.

```python
from textual.widgets.text_area import TextArea

text_area = TextArea()
text_area.show_line_numbers = True
text_area.line_number_start = 1
```

